{"tid":152964,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"點解有人會認為桌球唔係運動？","createTime":"2017-03-12T08:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T05:55:34.000Z","uid":84383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a7a2a835cbfbdcacee09136b924dab80cb580200","tid":152964,"uid":84383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:29:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e5jDspIC4hY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3De5jDspIC4hY&d=c1rUz8TxCzzDRK4zYpKqdDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=f3f55b56\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e5jDspIC4hY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實運動既定義唔一定要同體能有關，唔一定要流汗。<br />\n相反桌球同好多比較普及既運動一樣，都有好長既歷史文化，<br />\n都需要訓練，都有正規正式既比賽，都有當中既知識同技巧。<br />\n<br />\n當電子競技都叫e sports既時候。點解仲有人會認為桌球唔算運動？<br />\n<br />\n每日去波樓對住張波檯8個鐘。不斷做重覆既動作。比賽對住世界最top既一群職業選手。<br />\n其實就同足球籃球一樣。以上都係身為一個運動員需要面對既事。<br />\n只不過玩法唔同，同埋唔夠普及。<br />\n<br />\n但絕對唔影響桌球係一種運動呢個事實。"},{"pid":"b75d00013ccff0e13a08a8fdd38062c037fc2bf9","tid":152964,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:35:59.000Z","msg":"想知點解桌球男子成績好過女子咁多<br />\n外行人睇落 男女體格差異影響好細"},{"pid":"3d204504595f5c9d5cdab9aec70b5c965a8e5a34","tid":152964,"uid":84383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:48:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想知點解桌球男子成績好過女子咁多<br />\n外行人睇落 男女體格差異影響好細</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得係太少女仔接觸。<br />\n你可以睇下吳安儀。佢都係因為屋企人關係先接觸桌球。<br />\n如果唔係既話，甚至無人會將女性同桌球聯想埋一齊。"},{"pid":"d0177c8b4a100521fcab07ea51854596a5a22272","tid":152964,"uid":21972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:50:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想知點解桌球男子成績好過女子咁多<br />\n外行人睇落 男女體格差異影響好細</blockquote><br />\n力度應該係其中一樣<br />\n當準繩度一樣<br />\n但力度會影響球手炸散紅波，較波<br />\n呢兩樣已經可以改變到成個frame既走勢"},{"pid":"7422d3ec17ec24949d3704133db6e0a9dab9032d","tid":152964,"uid":84383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:55:04.000Z","msg":"莫講話女仔，宜家呢代甚至連男仔都唔多接觸。<br />\n<br />\n除左無乜推廣之外<br />\n波樓比人形象好雜，而且貴。比起就咁買一個籃球足球成本高。如果一個人去玩可能每次都要7,80蚊落樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外個人仲感覺到一種無形既壓力，來自於你隔離檯既人。你隔離檯既人多數係3,40歲既啊叔。你會感覺到自己同佢地差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"687151bc7d46c1e0f71b6e7bab21971bbbbd0d13","tid":152964,"uid":84383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:56:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想知點解桌球男子成績好過女子咁多<br />\n外行人睇落 男女體格差異影響好細</blockquote><br />\n力度應該係其中一樣<br />\n當準繩度一樣<br />\n但力度會影響球手炸散紅波，較波<br />\n呢兩樣已經可以改變到成個frame既走勢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有身高， 我有個男仔朋友比較矮。連攞住枝que都唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7047e8ba2b301fcae7e0401b5ce46773cbc7dec","tid":152964,"uid":21972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:03:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>莫講話女仔，宜家呢代甚至連男仔都唔多接觸。<br />\n<br />\n除左無乜推廣之外<br />\n波樓比人形象好雜，而且貴。比起就咁買一個籃球足球成本高。如果一個人去玩可能每次都要7,80蚊落樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外個人仲感覺到一種無形既壓力，來自於你隔離檯既人。你隔離檯既人多數係3,40歲既啊叔。你會感覺到自己同佢地差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n壓力係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多時都係搵d冇乜人既場，或者揀張附近冇人既檯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edeb82fb90ef5c35ff70f469b35ad1ea072e4f88","tid":152964,"uid":5684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:08:56.000Z","msg":"你叫班話卓球唔係運動既人揸住枝棍打幾局睇下手震唔震<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284dc2892dbd11377fb42f5deb1061923f7f62c6","tid":152964,"uid":84383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:10:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>莫講話女仔，宜家呢代甚至連男仔都唔多接觸。<br />\n<br />\n除左無乜推廣之外<br />\n波樓比人形象好雜，而且貴。比起就咁買一個籃球足球成本高。如果一個人去玩可能每次都要7,80蚊落樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外個人仲感覺到一種無形既壓力，來自於你隔離檯既人。你隔離檯既人多數係3,40歲既啊叔。你會感覺到自己同佢地差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n壓力係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多時都係搵d冇乜人既場，或者揀張附近冇人既檯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係好可惜，明明係個好好既運動但係搞到咁難接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n我平時揀最平既時段，又叫多啲朋友去，有壓力都盡量克服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1411961156b9c5b4d64dd03815400658986895cd","tid":152964,"uid":84383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:11:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你叫班話卓球唔係運動既人揸住枝棍打幾局睇下手震唔震<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n莫講話幾局 <br />\n班人唔識玩既打一局都可以打兩個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n打桌球幾曬精神真係打過先知"},{"pid":"e5c049657a862f1815834a5234db34df1b5f6472","tid":152964,"uid":21972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:23:26.000Z","msg":"題外話<br />\n有咩方法可以提升基本功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家1q頂籠得幾度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be876e5193a14ac9484b768cc70d42214748f77","tid":152964,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:53:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>題外話<br />\n有咩方法可以提升基本功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家1q頂籠得幾度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n操練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b087a7dff58fd8a5fdaaf6060804c4fc9f29206d","tid":152964,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:57:26.000Z","msg":"其實長期烏低個身對腰骨都唔好<br />\n特別係高佬"},{"pid":"b6e2d3661cb679cfaf75e86c45b3249bb5b1d005","tid":152964,"uid":77277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T10:03:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>題外話<br />\n有咩方法可以提升基本功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家1q頂籠得幾度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n操練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n基本功話明基本功<br />\n<br />\n只可以不停練習出cue練返黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講，即係打個手感出黎"},{"pid":"c6449b4ef87518e374c8c70a89247ba637e17381","tid":152964,"uid":84383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T10:25:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>題外話<br />\n有咩方法可以提升基本功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家1q頂籠得幾度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n操練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n基本功話明基本功<br />\n<br />\n只可以不停練習出cue練返黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講，即係打個手感出黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagger，有關知識係得咁多。<br />\n最主要都係打多啲。先捉到個種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c0ac64bb9882087b41650789ff1a4cee369cfa","tid":152964,"uid":55721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T05:55:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想知點解桌球男子成績好過女子咁多<br />\n外行人睇落 男女體格差異影響好細</blockquote><br />\n力度應該係其中一樣<br />\n當準繩度一樣<br />\n但力度會影響球手炸散紅波，較波<br />\n呢兩樣已經可以改變到成個frame既走勢</blockquote><br />\n咪玩啦，關乜事<br />\nMarco冇cue power咪一樣打到世界級<br />\nSteve Davis都講過女同男打桌球係冇分別<br />\n女冇成績係因為女人唔會晒咁多時間練